{"data":[{"date":"Th\u1ee9 Hai, ng\u00e0y 26/02/2018 04:37 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 26/2: \"Pogba \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00ec MU... thi\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi\"","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-941157\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-941157\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>\"Pogba ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh do MU... thi\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi\":</strong> Sau nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb HLV Jose Mourinho c\u1ea5t l\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb ho\u1eb7c r\u00fat ra s\u00e2n s\u1edbm, Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh \u1edf&nbsp;tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat. Tuy nhi\u00ean,&nbsp;Graeme Souness - c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Liverpool v\u1eabn h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ch\u00ea bai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed cho r\u1eb1ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh x\u1ebfp c\u1eadu tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Mourinho v\u00ec Ander Herrera d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng (r\u1eddi s\u00e2n gi\u1eefa ch\u1eebng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Sevilla&nbsp;tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc).</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 26/2: &amp;#34;Pogba \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00ec MU... thi\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi&amp;#34; - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-26/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-26-2----1519589228-684-width660height439.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Pogba \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat tr\u1eadn MU-Chelsea</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\"Trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, Pogba s\u1ebd t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed y\u00eau th\u00edch, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i hay ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai tr\u1ebb \u0111ang r\u1ed1i b\u1eddi, m\u1ea5t ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t v\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng bi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh x\u1ebfp c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn MU - Chelsea c\u1ee7a Mourinho \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00ec Herrera d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 th\u00f4i\".</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Barca m\u1ea5t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Chelsea:</strong> Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb Goal, Nelson Semedo \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Barca v\u00e0 Girona thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 25 La Liga (th\u1eafng 6-1) v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi xa s\u00e2n c\u1ecf 5 tu\u1ea7n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a, Barca s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Atletico (La Liga, 4/3) v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Chelsea (15/3, l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Harry Kane c\u00e1n m\u1ed1c 150 b\u00e0n cho Tottenham: </strong>Pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf ph\u00fat 89, \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Crystal Palace l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 150 c\u1ee7a&nbsp;Harry Kane trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o&nbsp;Tottenham. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1eady, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn derby London c\u1ee7a Didier Drogba (23 b\u00e0n/64 tr\u1eadn), \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Mohamed Salah (23 b\u00e0n) trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u \"Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Premier League\" (24 b\u00e0n).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>D\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5m, c\u1ef1u sao Arsenal b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 1 n\u0103m: </strong>Marca \u0111\u01b0a tin, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7&nbsp;Samir Nasri s\u1eafp nh\u1eadn \u00e1n&nbsp;treo gi\u00f2 6 th\u00e1ng v\u00ec d\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5m. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal, Man City b\u1ecb ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng li\u1ec7u ph\u00e1p truy\u1ec1n dung d\u1ecbch IV v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2017 khi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Sevilla theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Man City. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea1ng vitamin \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 gi\u1eef th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\u1ee6y ban ch\u1ed1ng doping th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi li\u1ec7t vi\u1ec7c truy\u1ec1n dung d\u1ecbch IV v\u00e0o danh m\u1ee5c c\u1ea5m t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2015. Ban \u0111\u1ea7u, \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Nasri l\u00e0&nbsp;2 n\u0103m nh\u01b0ng&nbsp;sau khi \u0111\u00e2m \u0111\u01a1n kh\u00e1ng \u00e1n l\u00ean T\u00f2a \u00e1n tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u1ec3 thao, ng\u00f4i sao 31 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3m \u00e1n.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Juventus b\u1ecb ho\u00e3n v\u00ec th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft:</strong> Cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u&nbsp;gi\u1eefa Juventus v\u00e0 Atalanta thu\u1ed9c khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 26 Serie A \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1ecb ho\u00e3n v\u00ec tuy\u1ebft r\u01a1i qu\u00e1 d\u00e0y. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, BTC Serie A v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m di\u1ec5n ra tr\u1eadn&nbsp;\u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, Juventus v\u00e0 Atalanta ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Coppa Italia c\u0169ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a \"B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\".</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"MU - Chelsea: \u201dVoi r\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec7 nh\u1ecb\u201d l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-25/1519570379-435-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">MU - Chelsea: \u201dVoi r\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec7 nh\u1ecb\u201d l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>\u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa MU v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh, h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-26-2-pogba-da-chinh-vi-mu-thieu-nguoi-c409a941157.html","id":"392"},{"date":"Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt, ng\u00e0y 25/02/2018 04:54 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 25/2: Anh s\u1eafp chi\u1ebfm quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2022","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-940982\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-940982\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2022 c\u1ee7a Qatar:</strong> Theo t\u1edd Mirror, FIFA ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u1edbc quy\u1ec1n t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u00fap th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 4 n\u0103m n\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Qatar do \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Trung \u0110\u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang v\u01b0\u1edbng nghi \u00e1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n cho nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u00e1c SV\u0110 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Anh v\u00e0 M\u1ef9 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u0103ng cai<strong> World Cup 2022</strong> n\u1ebfu FIFA c\u1eaft su\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Qatar.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 25/2: Anh s\u1eafp chi\u1ebfm quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2022 - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-25/Tin-bong-da-HOT-sang-25-2-World-Cup-2022-co-the-doi-nuoc-chu-nha-al-bayt-stadium-qatar-11-1519505506-833-width660height447.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Quang c\u1ea3nh tr\u00e1ng l\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t SV\u0110 \u1edf World Cup 2022 m\u00e0 Qatar d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\u00d4ng ch\u1ee7 Chelsea chi \u0111\u1eadm gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Hazard: </strong>Theo Don Balon, do kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t Eden Hazard n\u00ean \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n t\u1ef7 ph\u00fa ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga Roman Abramovich \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c. \u00d4ng ch\u1ee7 Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Hazard hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2020 v\u1edbi Chelsea nh\u01b0ng Real Madrid lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 anh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PSG mua \u201cTi\u1ec3u Buffon\u201d v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u euro: </strong>B\u00e1o Quotidiano Sportivo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Gianluigi Donnarumma \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Milan trong m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 19 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh \u201cTi\u1ec3u Buffon\u201d s\u1ebd l\u00e0 PSG. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0u th\u00e0nh Paris c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i chi ra \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\u201cMessi Ai C\u1eadp\u201d l\u1eadp k\u1ec9 l\u1ee5c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng:</strong> Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng West Ham 4-1 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi chi\u1ebfm ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi MU g\u1eb7p Chelsea \u1edf v\u00f2ng 28 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh t\u1ed1i nay (21h05, 25/2). \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, Mohamed Salah v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng cho \u201cThe Kop\u201d \u1edf ph\u00fat 51 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Anfield v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 20 b\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u201cMessi Ai C\u1eadp\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Liverpool c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a n\u00e0y c\u00e1n m\u1ed1c 100 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng (sau Man City, 111 b\u00e0n).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ghen t\u1ecb v\u1edbi 2 \u201cl\u00ednh m\u1edbi\u201d, sao Arsenal \u0111\u00f2i t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng:</strong>&nbsp;Theo t\u1edd The Times, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aaron Ramsey \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u BL\u0110 \u201cPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7\u201d tr\u1ea3 th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng (hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ee9c 110 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n) n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n anh k\u00ed h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Arsenal (Pierre Emerick Aubameyang v\u00e0 Henrikh Mkhitaryan) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 m\u1ee9c 170 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 24/2: Torres t\u00ednh chia tay Atletico ngay v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-24/t1-1519470019-540-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 24/2: Torres t\u00ednh chia tay Atletico ngay v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt HOT t\u1ed1i 24/2: Torres t\u00ednh chia tay Atletico ngay v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-25-2-anh-sap-chiem-quyen-dang-cai-world-cup-2022-c409a940982.html","id":"391"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y, ng\u00e0y 24/02/2018 05:05 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: \u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Balotelli th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Pogba?","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-940789\"></span>