2F%2Fpubads.g.doubleclick.net%2Fgampad%2Fads%3Fsz%3D528x297%26iu%3D%2F124557882%2F24h%2Fus%2Fdesktop%2Ffootball%2Fpostroll%26impl%3Ds%26gdfp_req%3D1%26env%3Dvp%26output%3Dvast%26unviewed_position_start%3D1%26url%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fus.24h.com.vn%252Ftin-van-bong-da%252Fchuyen-nhuong-mu-dong-doi-balotelli-the-cho-pogba-c409a940789.html%26description_url%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fus.24h.com.vn%252Ftin-van-bong-da%252Fchuyen-nhuong-mu-dong-doi-balotelli-the-cho-pogba-c409a940789.html%26correlator%3D1519425005%26ambient%3D1&ad_postrollOnly=0&ad_postrollTime=30&ad_postrollType=adsense&file=http://video-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/videoclip/2018-01-19/1516312124-jean-micha--l-seri.mp4&fileAlt=&image=http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-01-19/1516312124-jean-micha--l-seri.jpg&autoReEnableMini=1&volume=40&ad_volume=40&title=Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: \u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Balotelli th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Pogba?&ad_skipButton=1&mute=unmute&ad_mute=unmute&autoPlay=0\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%\"></div></div><!--end:str_video_player--></div><div id=\"pinListzplayer_78a351\" ></div><!--Begin:position_banner_sponsor_video--><!--End:position_banner_sponsor_video--><div id=\"zplayer_78a351_ga_preroll\" style=\"display:none\"></div><div id=\"zplayer_78a351_ga_postroll\" style=\"display:none\"></div><div id=\"zplayer_78a351_ga_overlay\" style=\"display:none\"></div><div id=\"zplayer_78a351_ga_started\" style=\"display:none\"></div><div id=\"zplayer_78a351_ga_doi_tac\" style=\"display:none\"></div></div><!-- end_media_player \r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Nh\u1eafm \u201cYaya Toure m\u1edbi\u201d thay th\u1ebf Pogba</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo t\u1edd Daily Mirror, <strong>MU</strong> \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u1edbi th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Paul Pogba khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang d\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m tin n\u01a1i HLV Jose Mourinho. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 6 c\u1ee7a \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb g\u1ea1t kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Huddersfield (gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng) v\u00e0 Sevilla (Champions League) v\u1eeba qua.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>MU</em>&nbsp;c\u0169ng v\u1eeba c\u1eed tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn Nga theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Lokomotiv Moscow v\u00e0 Nice \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng 1/16 Europa League h\u00f4m 22/2 v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i Jean Michael-Seri.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: \u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Balotelli th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Pogba? - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-24/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Xem-gio-dong-doi-trai-hu-Balotelli-de-the-cho-Pogba-reu_2390182-1519418487-829-width660height480.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Michael-Seri (Nice) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU r\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 \u201cYaya Toure m\u1edbi\u201d c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 v\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u201csi\u00eau qu\u1eady\u201d Mario Balotelli \u1edf Nice. Michael-Seri c\u0169ng t\u1eebng su\u00fdt c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 thay Pogba trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Nice hi\u1ec7n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>S\u1eafp \u201ctr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n\u201d De Gea th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>C\u00e2y vi\u1ebft uy t\u00edn Paul Hirst c\u1ee7a t\u1edd The Times v\u1eeba kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00f4ng tin David De Gea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi <u>MU</u> cho ph\u00e9p anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020 b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c Real Madrid v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ec7n\u201d n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh\u1edd b\u00e1o Ciaran Kelly c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Manchester Evening News th\u00ec cho bi\u1ebft th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 27 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01a1n 220.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n khi cam k\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><div style=\"text-align: center;width: 100%;clear: both;position: relative;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"position:relative;max-width: 660px;margin: 0 auto\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: \u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Balotelli th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Pogba? - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-24/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Xem-gio-dong-doi-trai-hu-Balotelli-de-the-cho-Pogba-a50536491b8214dec2f81a3c7128e100_crop_exact-1519418487-325-width660height440.jpg\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image\" style=\"position: absolute;display: block;overflow: hidden;width: 660px;height: 90px;color: white;bottom: 0px;left: 0px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image-close\" style=\"top:5px;right: 5px;position: absolute;display: none;overflow: hidden;width: 22px;height: 22px;color: #ccc;font-size: large;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: \u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Balotelli th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Pogba? - 3\" onclick=\"in_image_close();\" id=\"in-image-close\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/24h_banner_image_library/in-image-close.svg\"></img>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n                \r\n            </div></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">De Gea c\u1ee9u nguy cho MU tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Sevilla</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>D\u00f9ng 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00e2u sao Tottenham</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>T\u1edd The Times cho hay, MU ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Toby Alderweireld h\u00e8 n\u00e0y khi Tottenham s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u201cG\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng th\u00e0nh London\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 m\u00e0 \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n anh v\u1ec1 \u201cNh\u00e0 h\u00e1t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1\u201d s\u1ebd l\u00ean t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Gia nh\u1eadp MU, Alderweireld c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u con s\u1ed1 75.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf Tottenham hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Martial \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra \u0111i v\u00ec Sanchez</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>K\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh RMC Sport (Ph\u00e1p) \u0111\u01b0a tin cho bi\u1ebft Anthony Martial v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2019 s\u1ebd h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi c\u1ef1u ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a AS Monaco \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Old Trafford b\u1ecb \u0111e d\u1ecda khi c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh Alexis Sanchez. Hi\u1ec7n Tottenham, Inter Milan v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Real Madrid \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Martial.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i tin Rashford c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Martial, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Marcus Rashford \u1edf MU v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf khi Alexis Sanchez gia nh\u1eadp CLB n\u00e0y t\u1eeb Arsenal v\u00e0 chi\u00eam lu\u00f4n su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i Ladbrokes \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ra k\u00e8o tin r\u1eb1ng Rashford c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 r\u1ea5t cao 2/1 (\u0111\u1eb7t 1 \u0103n 2), theo sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Real Madrid v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 5/2 (\u0111\u1eb7t 2 \u0103n 5).</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"MU lo\u1ea1n v\u00ec Pogba - Mourinho: Si\u00eau c\u00f2 ra tay, Real &amp; Barca \u201dth\u1ea3 c\u00e2u\u201d\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-23/mu1-1519340839-8-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">MU lo\u1ea1n v\u00ec Pogba - Mourinho: Si\u00eau c\u00f2 ra tay, Real &amp; Barca \u201dth\u1ea3 c\u00e2u\u201d</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Nh\u00e2n l\u00fac MU \u0111ang r\u1ed1i ren, Real &amp; Barcelona s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u201c\u0111\u00e1nh c\u1eafp\u201d Pogba.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"chuyen-nhuong-mu-dong-doi-balotelli-the-cho-pogba-c409a940789.html","id":"390"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u, ng\u00e0y 23/02/2018 05:05 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 23/2: Gareth Bale l\u00e0 \"c\u00e1i gai\" c\u1ee7a Real","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-940533\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-940533\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Gareth Bale l\u00e0 \"c\u00e1i gai\" c\u1ee7a Real.</strong> Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales&nbsp;\u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb Real 3 trong 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. T\u1ec7 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, trong 19 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 qua c\u1ee7a CLB, Bale kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i tr\u1ecdn n\u1ed5i 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o. Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb AS (T\u00e2y Ban Nha), Gareth Bale hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \"c\u00e1i gai\" c\u1ee7a Real Madrid v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 23/2: Gareth Bale l\u00e0 &amp;#34;c\u00e1i gai&amp;#34; c\u1ee7a Real - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-22/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-23-2-Gareth-Bale-la-bale2-1519318747-969-width660height372.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Qu\u1ef9 th\u1eddi gian Real d\u00e0nh cho Bale \u0111ang s\u1eafp h\u1ebft</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mkhitaryan ca ng\u1ee3i l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 Arsenal. </strong>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Mkhitaryan kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn khi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a anh. \u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u1edbi th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Arsenal. B\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t y\u00eau b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Con s\u1ed1 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u201ckh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp\u201d c\u1ee7a De Gea.</strong> Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, De Gea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Luis Muriel. Theo s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u \u0111o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh (\u1edf c\u1ef1 ly 6 m\u00e9t) c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia \u0111\u1ea1t v\u1eadn t\u1ed1c 48m/ph. Nh\u01b0ng De Gea ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 0,26 gi\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 (b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a m\u00e8o). \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Hazard \u0111\u00f2i Conte tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng</strong>. \u201cT\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung t\u00e2m. Tuy nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n ch\u1ec9 ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng khi ch\u01a1i r\u1ed9ng, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh h\u01a1n. M\u1ed9t khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gian v\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean nguy hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n. Nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 do HLV \u0111\u01b0a ra, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\u201d Hazard chia s\u1ebb.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Barca gi\u1ea3m 1,2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 1 th\u00e1ng. </strong>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean m\u00e0 Barcelona h\u00f2a t\u1edbi 3 trong 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y khi s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng gi\u1ea3m s\u00fat. Ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Valverde \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 80 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 31 tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o trung b\u00ecnh 2,58 b\u00e0n m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong 1 th\u00e1ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3m, Barcelona ch\u1ec9 ghi trung b\u00ecnh 1,37 b\u00e0n m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn, c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalunya \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3m 1,2 b\u00e0n m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"\u201cBom t\u1ea5n\u201d MU b\u1ecb C\u00f4ng Vinh lo\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng tay: Lee Nguy\u1ec5n, Denilson c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u201ckh\u00f3c\u201d\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-22/1519307412-625-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">\u201cBom t\u1ea5n\u201d MU b\u1ecb C\u00f4ng Vinh lo\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng tay: Lee Nguy\u1ec5n, Denilson c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u201ckh\u00f3c\u201d</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>CLB TP. HCM quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU, Rodrigo Possebon.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-23-2-gareth-bale-la-cai-gai-cua-real-c409a940533.html","id":"389"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 N\u0103m, ng\u00e0y 22/02/2018 00:55 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 22/2: Liverpool g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Real Madrid","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-940299\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-940299\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Liverpool g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Real Madrid.</strong> Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Simon Mignolet r\u1eddi Anfield, Liverpool s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Theo Diario Gol, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch h\u1ecfi mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Keylor Navas c\u1ee7a Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 22/2: Liverpool g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Real Madrid - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-21/Tin-HOT-bong-da-22-2-Liverpool-gay-soc-voi-thu-mon-Real-Madrid-navas1-1519224896-576-width660height368.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Keylor Navas</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Barca v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Neymar.</strong> Sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 gi\u1eefa Chelsea v\u00e0 Barca, Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar. \u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Barca kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1eeb khi Neymar ra \u0111i, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1ecd c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 <strong>tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u01b0ng Barca v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Messi, Andres Iniesta v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Luis Suarez n\u1eefa.\u201d</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Arsenal nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb Aaron Ramsey. </strong>Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a \u201cPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7\u201d, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, anh t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 sung s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tham gia v\u00e0o c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp. H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i cho th\u1ea5y anh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man City v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 tin r\u1ea5t m\u1eebng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates b\u1edfi Ramsey l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Bayern san b\u1eb1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp sau 38 n\u0103m.</strong> Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Besiktas \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng gi\u00fap Bayern \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft m\u00e0 c\u00f2n san b\u1eb1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i 38 n\u0103m. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 14 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Bayern, san b\u1eb1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng d\u00e0i nh\u1ea5t m\u1ecdi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1980.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Coutinho tr\u1ea3i qua 24 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean \u1edf Barcelona. </strong>T\u00e2n binh Philippe Coutinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 24 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Champions League, b\u1ecb c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t Barcelona b\u1eaft xe v\u00e0 c\u00f2n b\u1ecb tr\u1ed9m \u0111\u1ed9t nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o nh\u00e0.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Chelsea c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Barca: Bi\u1ebfn Messi th\u00e0nh \u201dng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng\u201d, ph\u1ee5c th\u00f9 \u1edf Nou Camp\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-21/640che1-1519200261-542-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Chelsea c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Barca: Bi\u1ebfn Messi th\u00e0nh \u201dng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng\u201d, ph\u1ee5c th\u00f9 \u1edf Nou Camp</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \"b\u1eaft th\u00f3p\" Barca v\u00e0 c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n hy v\u1ecdng gi\u1eadt v\u00e9 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft t\u1ea1i Nou Camp.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-22-2-liverpool-gay-soc-voi-thu-mon-real-madrid-c409a940299.html","id":"388"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 T\u01b0, ng\u00e0y 21/02/2018 00:06 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 21/2: Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb d\u00f9 phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u1ee7ng","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-940097\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-940097\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb d\u00f9 phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u1ee7ng:</strong> Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 10 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t cho Real Madrid. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p th\u1ebf, tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Leganes (\u0111\u00e1 b\u00f9 v\u00f2ng 16 La Liga v\u00e0o 0h45, r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai 22/2), HLV Zidane n\u00f3i: \u201cRonaldo bao n\u0103m qua \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a 60 ho\u1eb7c 70 tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, \u0111\u00f4i khi ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 21/2: Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb d\u00f9 phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u1ee7ng - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-20/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-21-2-Ronaldo-co-the-du-bi-du-phong-do-khung-ronaldo-1519142443-475-width660height439.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>L\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Arsenal kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eafm Ancelotti thay Wenger:</strong> Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb t\u1edd Mirror, Arsenal s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd ch\u1ecdn Ancelotti, v\u00ec h\u1ecd s\u1ebd nh\u1eafm ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n. \u201cPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7\u201d mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t HLV tr\u1ebb thay v\u00ec b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 58 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Ancelotti, v\u00e0 c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thay v\u00ec m\u1ed9t HLV li\u00ean t\u1ee5c thay \u0111\u1ed5i CLB nh\u01b0 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>HLV Kloop chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 h\u1ed3i sinh c\u1ee7a Sadio Mane:</strong> \u201cL\u1eddi khuy\u00ean t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t lu\u00f4n t\u1eeb ri\u00eang b\u1ea1n. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng \u1edf trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n ai \u0111\u00f3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3? Quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 Mane c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 quen v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, mi\u1ec5n l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u00e1y m\u00f3c v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean xu\u1ed1ng\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Qu\u00fd t\u1eed nh\u00e0 Drogba gia nh\u1eadp Guingamp:</strong> Con trai c\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Didier Drogba, Isaac Drogba \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cha anh t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, Guingamp c\u1ee7a Ligue 1. Con trai c\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a Drogba, Isaac Drogba, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 \u201cVoi r\u1eebng\u201d v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c theo b\u01b0\u1edbc cha.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>S\u1ebfp b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 AFF Cup 2018:</strong> \u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ec7nh ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u1edf AFF Suzuki Cup 2018 nh\u1eb1m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. N\u1ebfu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, G\u0110KT Witthaya Laohakul s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tung ra l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c\u201d, \u00f4ng Witthaya chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Bangkok Post.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Ronaldo m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i \u201dvua l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng\u201d: \u0110\u1ed3ng ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111i li\u1ec1n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-01-26/sadfsdfs-----1516924625-981-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Ronaldo m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i \u201dvua l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng\u201d: \u0110\u1ed3ng ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111i li\u1ec1n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Ronaldo c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u si\u00eau sao kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 \"tr\u00ean tr\u1eddi\".</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-21-2-ronaldo-co-the-du-bi-du-phong-do-khung-c409a940097.html","id":"387"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 Ba, ng\u00e0y 20/02/2018 03:00 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 20/2: L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n th\u00eam \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean thay Conte","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-939867\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-939867\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n th\u00eam \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean thay Conte.</strong> Theo Football Italia, Chelsea \u0111ang ng\u1ea7m ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u1edbi HLV Massimiliano Allegri - ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i Italia, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus. T\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00e0y cho hay, Allegri s\u1ebd th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Conte t\u1ea1i Chelsea, nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng thay th\u1ebf \u1edf Juventus. Allegri t\u1eebng 4 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A, 3 v\u1edbi Juventus v\u00e0 1 v\u1edbi AC Milan.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 20/2: L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n th\u00eam \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean thay Conte - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-19/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-20-2-Lo-dien-them-ung-vien-thay-Conte-660-1519012964-185-width660height366.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">HLV Allegri s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf Conte t\u1ea1i Chelsea?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Bayern quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Vidal. </strong>H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Arturo Vidal v\u1edbi Bayern Munich ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2019. Hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Bayern \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Vidal gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gary Neville \u0111\u1eb7t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng \u1edf Ibrahimovic.</strong> N\u00f3i v\u1edbi Sky Sport, BLV Gary Neville cho bi\u1ebft, Zlatan Ibrahimovic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m chinh chi\u1ebfn \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng \u0111\u0103ng quang, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n MU tin r\u1eb1ng kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Ibrahimovic s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Arsenal tranh sao tr\u1ebb \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi MU.</strong> Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Timo Werner l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. \u1ede Confederations Cup 2017, Werner d\u00f9 m\u1edbi 21 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao bom t\u1ea5n nh\u01b0 Ronaldo, Sanchez \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o RB Leipzig, Werner c\u0169ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1. HLV Wenger mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Werner v\u1ec1 Emirates, d\u00f9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU theo \u0111u\u1ed5i g\u1eaft gao.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chelsea quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Hazard v\u00e0 Kante. </strong>Do n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, Chelsea \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8. Theo t\u1edd Telegraph, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 Thibaut Courtois, Eden Hazard hay N\u2019Golo Kante, cho d\u00f9 Real hay PSG c\u00f3 tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Bi k\u1ecbch HLV Chelsea: Kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn g\u01b0\u01a1ng Mourinho, Conte \u201d\u0111i\u1ebfc kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 s\u00fang\u201d\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-07/1517995836-898-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Bi k\u1ecbch HLV Chelsea: Kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn g\u01b0\u01a1ng Mourinho, Conte \u201d\u0111i\u1ebfc kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 s\u00fang\u201d</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Chelsea c\u00f3 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng b\u1ea1c \u0111\u00e3i c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n n\u00ean Conte h\u00e3y li\u1ec7u ch\u1eebng t\u1ea5m g\u01b0\u01a1ng Mourinho.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-20-2-lo-dien-them-ung-vien-thay-conte-c409a939867.html","id":"386"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 Hai, ng\u00e0y 19/02/2018 05:30 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 19/2: HLV Conte \"l\u1eadt t\u1ea9y\" \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu Barcelona","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-939808\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-939808\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>HLV Conte ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Barcelona. </strong>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y,&nbsp;chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia Italia&nbsp;kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barcelona r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng khai th\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu n\u00e0y khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia t\u1ea1i Champions League.&nbsp;\"\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu khi kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng khai th\u00e1c tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 19/2: HLV Conte &amp;#34;l\u1eadt t\u1ea9y&amp;#34; \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu Barcelona - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-19/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-19-2-HLV-Conte-chi-ra-diem-yeu-lon-nhat-cua-Barcelona-c1-1518977069-326-width660height371.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">HLV Conte</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sao tr\u1ebb Man City \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1ea5p r\u01b0\u1ee1i. </strong>Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Zinchenko m\u1edbi l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Man City ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euro Danilo. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u1edfng Zinchenko, l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Man City \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch d\u00e0nh cho anh m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi ngay c\u1ea3 khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u0169 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2021. Trong \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ukraine c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh t\u1eeb 40 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 60 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Barcelona&nbsp;m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n sau khi b\u00e1n Neymar.&nbsp;</strong>Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Ter Stegen kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barcelona m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u d\u00f9 m\u1ea5t \u0111i ng\u00f4i sao Neymar \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua. \"D\u00f9 m\u1ea5t Neymar nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i t\u00e2n binh gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t&nbsp;h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. Hy v\u1ecdng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i khi ch\u01a1i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y.\"</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Hazard l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Real.&nbsp;</strong>Trong m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n tr\u00ean t\u1edd Telefoot m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Hazard \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u00f4i \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u201cTrong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. Nh\u01b0ng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra c\u1ea3. N\u0103m n\u00e0o h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Real ho\u1eb7c PSG. V\u00e0 khi m\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i CLB, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Chelsea.\"</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fabregas bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch khi\u1ebfn Barcelona ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.&nbsp;</strong>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u1edf Stamford Bridge v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Cesc Fabregas t\u1ef1 tin r\u1eb1ng anh&nbsp;bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Barcelona.&nbsp;\u201c\u0110\u00e2y&nbsp;v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB m\u1ea1nh. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u00e1p l\u1ef1c ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 v\u00ec v\u1eady, s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u1edf ph\u00eda sau. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, HLV Conte s\u1ebd t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1i \u01b0u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho thanh l\u00fd \u201dh\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n\u201d ki\u1ebfm 87 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-18/640mu-mou-1518972514-209-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho thanh l\u00fd \u201dh\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n\u201d ki\u1ebfm 87 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>HLV Jose Mourinho s\u1ebd m\u1ea1nh tay thanh l\u1ecdc l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng th\u00eam ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch mua s\u1eafm.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-19-2-hlv-conte-lat-tay-diem-yeu-barcelona-c409a939808.html","id":"385"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 Hai, ng\u00e0y 19/02/2018 00:04 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho thanh l\u00fd \"h\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n\" ki\u1ebfm 87 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-939794\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-939794\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>PSG h\u1ecfi mua Rojo 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>T\u1edd The Sun cho hay, Rojo \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a PSG. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0u n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea7n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 \u1ea2 r\u1eadp s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Old Trafford. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Rojo v\u1edbi MU ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2019.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho thanh l\u00fd &amp;#34;h\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n&amp;#34; ki\u1ebfm 87 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-18/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Mourinho-thanh-ly-mu-rojo-1518972388-7-width660height371.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">HLV Mourinho v\u00e0 Rojo</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Herrera \u0111\u1ebfn Milan, MU c\u00f3 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>AC Milan \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 h\u1ecfi mua Ander Herrera. Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Italia cho hay, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ebfn MU. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Mourinho. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho t\u00e2n binh Matic v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Arsenal h\u1ecfi Luke Shaw, Mourinho mu\u1ed1n 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 khi c\u00f3 th\u00eam Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 Aubameyang. H\u1ebft m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, HLV Wenger mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. Luke Shaw \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed c\u1ee7a \"Gi\u00e1o s\u01b0\" nh\u01b0ng MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n r\u1ebb. Daily Star cho hay, HLV Mourinho ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 Shaw ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ee7 mua m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi thay th\u1ebf.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Griezmann kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00ec Sanchez</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Sanchez k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 Griezmann. T\u1edd Don Balon cho hay, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Old Trafford khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Sanchez khi\u1ebfn anh lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y. Griezmann v\u00e0 Sanchez c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Atletico s\u1ebd \"h\u1ea1 c\u00e1nh\" xu\u1ed1ng Barca.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fellaini ch\u1ecdn xong b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fellaini l\u1ea1i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i n\u00ean MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi ngay t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. Mirror cho hay, Fellaini quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sang Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00f3c x\u00f9 l\u00e0 Besiktas.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"MU: Pogba b\u1ecb nghi kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Real, Mourinho ph\u1edbt l\u1edd\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-18/640x480-1518920275-635-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">MU: Pogba b\u1ecb nghi kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Real, Mourinho ph\u1edbt l\u1edd</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>MU th\u1eafng Huddersfield trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y Paul Pogba ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"chuyen-nhuong-mu-mourinho-thanh-ly-hang-ton-kiem-87-trieu-bang-c409a939794.html","id":"384"},{"date":"Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt, ng\u00e0y 18/02/2018 05:05 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 18/2: Carrick ch\u1ec9 ra truy\u1ec1n nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1i MU","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-939669\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-939669\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Carrick ch\u1ec9 ra truy\u1ec1n nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1i MU</strong><strong>.&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;Michael Carrick ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho MU \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam bao l\u00e2u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do v\u00ec sao ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf m\u00ecnh trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 Carrick \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp t\u1edbi trong ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Scott McTominay: \u201cScott l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o. McTominay c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc.\u201d</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 18/2: Carrick ch\u1ec9 ra truy\u1ec1n nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1i MU - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-18/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-18-2-Carrick-chi-ra-truyen-nhan-tai-MU-mu3-1518899893-347-width660height367.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Scott McTominay</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>D\u00e0n sao Liverpool sang T\u00e2y Ban Nha x\u1ea3 h\u01a1i.&nbsp;</strong>Do kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi FA Cup, ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n&nbsp;Liverpool quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sang T\u00e2y Ban Nha kho\u1ea3ng 4 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edfng \u00e1nh n\u1eafng \u1ea5m \u00e1p n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y. Chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i x\u1ea3 tr\u1ea1i sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Porto \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u1ea5t.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\" ch\u1ec9 ra nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Chelsea.&nbsp;</strong>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng khi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean l\u00e0m b\u1ea1n tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Chelsea, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cM\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Chelsea kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, t\u00f4i c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft HLV Conte c\u00f3 theo d\u00f5i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh hay kh\u00f4ng. Ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng r\u1ed3i quay l\u1ea1i gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng n\u00e0o.\"</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Xabi Alonso ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean tam t\u1ea5u Liverpool.&nbsp;</strong>C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i hoa ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ng\u1ee3i khen b\u1ed9 ba h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Mohamed Salah, Roberto Firmino v\u00e0 Sadio Mane c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169. \"Th\u1eadt ti\u1ebfc khi t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd v\u00ec c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 ba \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eeb ph\u00eda sau. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Jurgen Klopp, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Dortmund.\u201d</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Barca g\u1eb7p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Eibar.&nbsp;</strong>D\u00f9 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng HLV Ernesto Valverde th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Eibar l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 nh\u1eb1n: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c c\u0169ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Eibar \u0111\u1ea9y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0o th\u1ebf v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00f3 khi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 cao. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\".</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Huddersfield Town - MU: Uy l\u1ef1c kinh h\u1ed3n, c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap m\u00e3n nh\u00e3n\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-18/mu2-1518896932-726-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Huddersfield Town - MU: Uy l\u1ef1c kinh h\u1ed3n, c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap m\u00e3n nh\u00e3n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>M\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-18-2-carrick-chi-ra-truyen-nhan-tai-mu-c409a939669.html","id":"383"}]}